about.summary: PostgreSQL is a powerful, open source object-relational database system

name: postgresql
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "9.5.3" %}

package:
    name: postgresql
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: postgresql-{{ version }}.tar.bz2
    url: https://ftp.postgresql.org/pub/source/v{{ version }}/postgresql-{{ version }}.tar.bz2
    sha256: 7385c01dc58acba8d7ac4e6ad42782bd7c0b59272862a3a3d5fe378d4503a0b4
    patches:
        - fix_libraries_win.patch  # [win]

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [win]
    features:
        - vc9  # [win and py27]
        - vc10  # [win and py34]
        - vc14  # [win and py35]

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - openssl 1.0.*
        - perl  # [win]
        - zlib 1.2.*
    run:
        - python
        - openssl 1.0.*
        - zlib 1.2.*

test:
    commands:
        - pg_config
        - postgres --help

about:
    home: http://www.postgresql.org/
    license: PostgreSQL
    summary: PostgreSQL is a powerful, open source object-relational database system

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - msarahan
        - ocefpaf
